OL,3,CAlcohol deaths fall in Dumfries and
OL,4,CGalloway but rise in Scottish Borders
OL,6,FThe number of alcohol related deaths
OL,7,Fin Dumfries and Galloway has fallen in
OL,8,F2023 compared to 2022, whilst the
OL,9,Fnumber is on the rise in the Scottish
OL,10,FBorders.
OL,12,FThe figures released by the National
OL,13,FRecords of Scotland highlighted the
OL,14,Fnumber of people who have died as a
OL,15,Fresult of alcohol in 2023.
OL,17,FIn total there were 1,277 deaths
OL,18,Fcaused by alcohol in Scotland, an
OL,19,Fincrease of one from 2022.
